Package: chromploid
Title: Chromosome Number and Ploidy Evolution Models
Version: 0.0.1.0000
Authors@R: person("Rosana", "Zenil-Ferguson", email = "roszenil@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Likelihood calculation of models for chromosome number evolution
    associated to binary character and ploidy evolution models. Models included are
    BiChroM, BiChroM linear, PloidEvol, and ChromEvolM3.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.4)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    ape,
    expm,
    geiger,
    MASS
Suggests:
    phytools,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
